headline: Is Walgreens Stock a Buy?
summary: Walgreens is a large pharmacy retailer that has been struggling after making several bad strategic bets.  There's unlikely to be much upside from here for Walgreens.  Walgreens Boots Alliance (NASDAQ: WBA) is one of the largest pharmacy retailers in the United States.
